  <name>GamerX Store</name>
  <summary>GamerX Linux application store for Flatpak applications</summary>
  <description>
    <p>
      GamerX Store is the official application store for GamerX Linux, providing
      easy access to thousands of applications from Flathub and custom GamerX
      repositories.
    </p>
    <p>
      Built on modern GTK4 technology with smooth animations and a beautiful
      interface, GamerX Store makes it simple to discover, install, and manage
      applications on your GamerX Linux system.
    </p>
  </description>

  <developer id="io.github.gamerx">
    <name>GamerX Linux Team</name>
  </developer>

